item.title: You will never know what a short leg means to a dog.
item.author: youremail@domain.com (Some Person)
item.description: 2019-02-22 17:07:32 Source: Searchwood Report As a short-legged dog, there are too many regrets and too many wishes that cannot be fulfilled in this life. First of all, not being able to experience the sense of accomplishment that jumping brings to a dog! When you’re camping with your buddies, running through the jungle, enjoying the summer breeze, it doesn’t take long for you to discover a blow that’s too much for a dog to handle.
